<div class="format_text" id="comment-body-921">
<p>This article states that New Mexico doesn&#8217;t ask and doesn&#8217;t publish the owners of the New Mexico LLC, however a very brief search on the Internet reveals the New Mexico Division of Corporations where one can indeed look up LLCs and Corporations and can indeed see the officers and/or members.</p>
<p><a href="http://164.64.53.200/CorpSearch/(S(wlvo4d55lsdz3qntyjoim545)" rel="nofollow">http://164.64.53.200/CorpSearch/(S(wlvo4d55lsdz3qntyjoim545)</a>)/CorpSearch.aspx</p>
